{"comments":"Audio Trigger — Event-based audio playback for UI feedback.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nAudio triggers are declarative descriptions of when and how to play\nsounds in response to UI events. The runtime handles actual playback.\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- Hover sounds (dog bark on hover over dog card)\n- Click feedback (button press sounds)\n- Enter/exit sounds (slide transitions)\n- Achievement sounds (gamification)\n- Error/success feedback\n\n## Audio Behavior\n\n- Play once vs loop\n- Fade in/out\n- Volume control\n- Delay before playing\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Schema.Audio.Level (volume)\n- Schema.Dimension.Temporal (delay, fade duration)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/Trigger.purs","start":[89,3]},"title":"AudioUrl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/Trigger.purs","start":[90,3]},"title":"AudioInline"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","Trigger"],"AudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/Trigger.purs","start":[92,1]},"title":"eqAudioSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","Trigger"],"AudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,50],"na